commit.message:
Added Learn Script
The learn script will go to message that have been asked, collect the reply in the thread, and update Mongo with the response
Changed picture to a single obj.
Added the path for pictures.
Made the model more inline with json schema.
Combined and refactored models into 1 file.
rudimentary data models made

Added Ask Script
The ask script will go through each user and find a question to ask them, then sent them a message on Slack

Successfully add users to Mongo
We can now successfully add users who aren't in Mongo to Mongo

Mongo and Handle Message
Added a connection to Mongo on localhost:27017 and started handling messages directed at Dfacto
Added function to parse message, channel, and user from Slack RTM
added json models that need to be fleshed out
Add requirements
